<template>
 
<router-view/>

</template>

<script>
import { onMounted } from 'vue';
import $ from 'jquery'

export default {
    name: "App",
    setup(){
        var $,jquery = require('jquery')

        onMounted(()=>{
                setTimeout(() => {
                const jspath = 'js/';
                var jslibs = ['bootstrap.min.js', 'jquery.countdown.js', 'jquery.fullPage.min.js', 'jquery.appear.js', 'jquery.fitvids.js', 'jquery.backstretch.min.js', 'owl.carousel.min.js', 'jquery.ajaxchimp.js', 'particles.js', 'moment.js','main.js'];
                for(var i=0;i<14;i++){
                var customLib = document.createElement("script");
                customLib.setAttribute('src',jspath+jslibs[i]);
                document.body.appendChild(customLib);
                }
            }, 1000);

            $("body").tooltip({
                selector: '[data-toggle=tooltip]'
            });

        });

        

        return {}
    }
}
</script>

<style>
</style>
